# Cloudflare Pages SPA Redirect
# This ensures React Router works properly with client-side routing
#
# NOTE: Do NOT use 200 rewrites to .html files for specific paths.
# Cloudflare Pages' clean-URL feature will 308-redirect them instead
# of serving the content in-place. The /* wildcard is special-cased
# by Pages as an SPA fallback and works correctly.

# Landing page as homepage until launch (302 because 200 rewrite
# to landing.html triggers a 308 clean-URL redirect)
/ /landing 302

# SPA fallback — serves React app for all other routes
# (including /sign-in, /sign-up)
/* /index.html 200
